<div class="title">Caffeine Sweats</div>
<div class="substance">Caffeine</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=AndrewR&Exact=1">AndrewR</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; AndrewR. "Caffeine Sweats: An Experience with Caffeine (exp10931)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Oct 29, 2003. erowid.org/exp/10931</div>

